Requirements:

- Work individually
- Render a game in the browser
- Use Git and Github (commit frequently, work with branches, use Pull Requests)
- Include separate HTML / CSS / JavaScript files
- Use jQuery for DOM manipulation
- Write clean code (proper indentation, comments explaining the code, spliting large code to functions...etc)
- Deploy your game online using Github Pages, where the rest of the world can access it
- Include a README.md with explanations of game instructions, unsolved problems...etc.
